{
  "book": "2nephi",
  "bookName": "2 Nephi",
  "chapter": 1,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "iJpuSZDxZSBJHFSeavba",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "sister-m"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 679.367,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 6.827,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now it came to pass that after I, Nephi, had made an end of teaching my brethren,",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 7.007,
      "end": 11.326,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "our father, Lehi, also spake many things unto them,",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 11.506,
      "end": 16.522,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and rehearsed unto them, how great things the Lord had done for them",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 16.702,
      "end": 19.813,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in bringing them out of the land of Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 20.493,
      "end": 22.072,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he spake unto them",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 22.252,
      "end": 25.178,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning their rebellions upon the waters,",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 25.358,
      "end": 28.841,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the mercies of God in sparing their lives,",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 29.021,
      "end": 31.9,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they were not swallowed up in the sea.",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 32.58,
      "end": 36.667,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he also spake unto them concerning the land of promise,",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 36.847,
      "end": 39.355,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which they had obtained\u2014",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 39.535,
      "end": 41.764,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "how merciful the Lord had been",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 41.944,
      "end": 46.356,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in warning us that we should flee out of the land of Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 47.036,
      "end": 48.94,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For, behold, said he,",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 49.12,
      "end": 50.606,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I have seen a vision,",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 50.786,
      "end": 54.037,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in which I know that Jerusalem is destroyed;",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 54.217,
      "end": 58.722,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and had we remained in Jerusalem we should also have perished.",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 59.402,
      "end": 63.396,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But, said he, notwithstanding our afflictions,",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 63.576,
      "end": 66.177,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we have obtained a land of promise,",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 66.357,
      "end": 69.654,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a land which is choice above all other lands;",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 69.834,
      "end": 73.317,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a land which the Lord God hath covenanted with me",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 73.497,
      "end": 77.398,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "should be a land for the inheritance of my seed.",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 77.578,
      "end": 83.987,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, the Lord hath covenanted this land unto me and to my children forever,",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 84.167,
      "end": 90.576,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also all those who should be led out of other countries by the hand of the Lord.",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 91.256,
      "end": 94.507,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, I, Lehi, prophesy",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 94.687,
      "end": 98.542,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the workings of the Spirit which is in me,",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 98.722,
      "end": 101.648,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that there shall none come into this land",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 101.828,
      "end": 105.775,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save they shall be brought by the hand of the Lord.",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 106.455,
      "end": 111.378,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, this land is consecrated unto him whom he shall bring.",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 111.558,
      "end": 114.53,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And if it so be that they shall serve him",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 114.71,
      "end": 117.682,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the commandments which he hath given,",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 117.862,
      "end": 121.066,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it shall be a land of liberty unto them;",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 121.246,
      "end": 125.147,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, they shall never be brought down into captivity;",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 125.327,
      "end": 128.299,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if so, it shall be because of iniquity;",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 128.479,
      "end": 130.847,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for if iniquity shall abound",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 131.027,
      "end": 133.86,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "cursed shall be the land for their sakes,",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 134.04,
      "end": 137.709,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but unto the righteous it shall be blessed forever.",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 138.389,
      "end": 141.175,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And behold, it is wisdom",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 141.355,
      "end": 146.742,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that this land should be kept as yet from the knowledge of other nations;",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 146.922,
      "end": 150.544,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for behold, many nations would overrun the land,",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 150.724,
      "end": 153.835,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that there would be no place for an inheritance.",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 154.515,
      "end": 158.555,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, I, Lehi, have obtained a promise",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 158.735,
      "end": 166.351,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that inasmuch as those whom the Lord God shall bring out of the land of Jerusalem shall keep his commandments,",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 166.531,
      "end": 169.735,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall prosper upon the face of this land;",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 169.915,
      "end": 173.491,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall be kept from all other nations,",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 173.671,
      "end": 177.015,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they may possess this land unto themselves.",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 177.195,
      "end": 180.864,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And if it so be that they shall keep his commandments",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 181.044,
      "end": 184.481,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall be blessed upon the face of this land,",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 184.661,
      "end": 187.401,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and there shall be none to molest them,",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 187.581,
      "end": 190.367,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nor to take away the land of their inheritance;",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 190.547,
      "end": 193.566,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall dwell safely forever.",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 194.246,
      "end": 196.893,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, when the time cometh",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 197.073,
      "end": 199.581,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they shall dwindle in unbelief,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 199.761,
      "end": 208.26,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after they have received so great blessings from the hand of the Lord\u2014",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 208.44,
      "end": 212.666,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "having a knowledge of the creation of the earth, and all men,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 212.846,
      "end": 218.326,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "knowing the great and marvelous works of the Lord from the creation of the world;",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 218.506,
      "end": 221.85,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "having power given them to do all things by faith;",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 222.03,
      "end": 224.956,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "having all the commandments from the beginning,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 225.136,
      "end": 228.48,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and having been brought by his infinite goodness",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 228.66,
      "end": 234.976,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "into this precious land of promise\u2014",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 235.156,
      "end": 238.453,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, I say, if the day shall come",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 238.633,
      "end": 241.977,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they will reject the Holy One of Israel,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 242.157,
      "end": 243.597,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the true Messiah,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 243.777,
      "end": 246.053,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "their Redeemer and their God,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 246.233,
      "end": 251.156,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, the judgments of him that is just shall rest upon them.",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 251.836,
      "end": 255.087,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, he will bring other nations unto them,",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 255.267,
      "end": 257.682,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he will give unto them power,",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 257.862,
      "end": 259.905,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he will take away from them",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 260.085,
      "end": 262.175,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the lands of their possessions,",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 262.355,
      "end": 265.931,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he will cause them to be scattered and smitten.",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 266.611,
      "end": 272.23,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, as one generation passeth to another there shall be bloodsheds,",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 272.41,
      "end": 274.825,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and great visitations among them;",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 275.005,
      "end": 278.581,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, my sons, I would that ye would remember;",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 278.761,
      "end": 283.173,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, I would that ye would hearken unto my words.",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 283.853,
      "end": 285.246,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O that ye would awake;",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 285.426,
      "end": 287.237,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "awake from a deep sleep,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 287.417,
      "end": 290.111,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even from the sleep of hell,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 290.291,
      "end": 294.006,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and shake off the awful chains by which ye are bound,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 294.186,
      "end": 297.762,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which are the chains which bind the children of men,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 297.942,
      "end": 308.948,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they are carried away captive",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 309.128,
      "end": 312.657,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "down to the eternal gulf of misery and woe.",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 313.337,
      "end": 316.356,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Awake! and arise from the dust,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 316.536,
      "end": 319.462,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and hear the words of a trembling parent,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 319.642,
      "end": 328.373,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whose limbs ye must soon lay down in the cold and silent grave,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 328.553,
      "end": 331.014,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from whence no traveler can return;",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 331.194,
      "end": 335.374,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a few more days and I go the way of all the earth.",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 336.054,
      "end": 339.676,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, the Lord hath redeemed my soul from hell;",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 339.856,
      "end": 341.76,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I have beheld his glory,",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 341.94,
      "end": 346.909,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I am encircled about eternally in the arms of his love.",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 347.589,
      "end": 350.468,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I desire that ye should remember",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 350.648,
      "end": 354.131,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to observe the statutes and the judgments of the Lord;",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 354.311,
      "end": 359.698,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, this hath been the anxiety of my soul from the beginning.",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 360.378,
      "end": 364.418,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "My heart hath been weighed down with sorrow from time to time,",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 364.598,
      "end": 366.131,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I have feared,",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 366.311,
      "end": 368.726,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "lest for the hardness of your hearts",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 368.906,
      "end": 371.6,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Lord your God should come out",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 371.78,
      "end": 374.381,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the fulness of his wrath upon you,",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 374.561,
      "end": 377.487,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that ye be cut off and destroyed forever;",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 378.167,
      "end": 383.693,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Or, that a cursing should come upon you for the space of many generations;",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 383.873,
      "end": 388.61,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and ye are visited by sword, and by famine, and are hated,",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 388.79,
      "end": 393.016,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and are led according to the will and captivity of the devil.",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 393.696,
      "end": 397.551,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O my sons,",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 397.731,
      "end": 400.564,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that these things might not come upon you,",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 400.744,
      "end": 405.109,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but that ye might be a choice and a favored people of the Lord.",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 405.289,
      "end": 407.425,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, his will be done;",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 407.605,
      "end": 410.531,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for his ways are righteousness forever.",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 411.211,
      "end": 413.161,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he hath said that:",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 413.341,
      "end": 416.545,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Inasmuch as ye shall keep my commandments",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 416.725,
      "end": 418.861,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye shall prosper in the land;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 419.041,
      "end": 422.663,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but inasmuch as ye will not keep my commandments",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 422.843,
      "end": 425.537,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye shall be cut off from my presence.",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 426.217,
      "end": 429.375,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now that my soul might have joy in you,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 429.555,
      "end": 434.478,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that my heart might leave this world with gladness because of you,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 434.658,
      "end": 442.367,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I might not be brought down with grief and sorrow to the grave,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 442.547,
      "end": 445.891,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "arise from the dust, my sons, and be men,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 446.071,
      "end": 452.526,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and be determined in one mind and in one heart, united in all things,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 452.706,
      "end": 455.585,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that ye may not come down into captivity;",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 456.265,
      "end": 459.469,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "That ye may not be cursed with a sore cursing;",
      "verse": "1:22",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 459.649,
      "end": 465.175,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also, that ye may not incur the displeasure of a just God upon you,",
      "verse": "1:22",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 465.355,
      "end": 467.166,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the destruction,",
      "verse": "1:22",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 467.346,
      "end": 472.083,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, the eternal destruction of both soul and body.",
      "verse": "1:22",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 472.763,
      "end": 474.203,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Awake, my sons;",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 474.383,
      "end": 476.984,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "put on the armor of righteousness.",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 477.164,
      "end": 480.508,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Shake off the chains with which ye are bound,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 480.688,
      "end": 483.242,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and come forth out of obscurity,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 483.422,
      "end": 485.419,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and arise from the dust.",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 486.099,
      "end": 488.7,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Rebel no more against your brother,",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 488.88,
      "end": 491.295,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whose views have been glorious,",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 491.475,
      "end": 496.026,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and who hath kept the commandments from the time that we left Jerusalem;",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 496.206,
      "end": 502.661,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and who hath been an instrument in the hands of God,",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 502.841,
      "end": 506.138,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in bringing us forth into the land of promise;",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 506.318,
      "end": 508.222,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for were it not for him,",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 508.402,
      "end": 512.117,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we must have perished with hunger in the wilderness;",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 512.297,
      "end": 515.78,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless, ye sought to take away his life;",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 137
    },
    {
      "start": 515.96,
      "end": 520.186,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, and he hath suffered much sorrow because of you.",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 520.866,
      "end": 524.488,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I exceedingly fear and tremble because of you,",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 524.668,
      "end": 526.572,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "lest he shall suffer again;",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 526.752,
      "end": 529.306,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for behold, ye have accused him",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 141
    },
    {
      "start": 529.486,
      "end": 532.551,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he sought power and authority over you;",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 142
    },
    {
      "start": 532.731,
      "end": 537.654,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but I know that he hath not sought for power nor authority over you,",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 143
    },
    {
      "start": 537.834,
      "end": 540.342,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but he hath sought the glory of God,",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 144
    },
    {
      "start": 540.522,
      "end": 542.705,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and your own eternal welfare.",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 145
    },
    {
      "start": 543.385,
      "end": 547.843,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And ye have murmured because he hath been plain unto you.",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 146
    },
    {
      "start": 548.023,
      "end": 550.67,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Ye say that he hath used sharpness;",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 147
    },
    {
      "start": 550.85,
      "end": 553.869,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye say that he hath been angry with you;",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 148
    },
    {
      "start": 554.049,
      "end": 556.232,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but behold, his sharpness",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 149
    },
    {
      "start": 556.412,
      "end": 559.756,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "was the sharpness of the power of the word of God,",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 150
    },
    {
      "start": 559.936,
      "end": 561.469,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which was in him;",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 151
    },
    {
      "start": 561.649,
      "end": 564.993,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that which ye call anger was the truth,",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 152
    },
    {
      "start": 565.173,
      "end": 567.356,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to that which is in God,",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 153
    },
    {
      "start": 567.536,
      "end": 569.44,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he could not restrain,",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 154
    },
    {
      "start": 569.62,
      "end": 573.057,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "manifesting boldly concerning your iniquities.",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 155
    },
    {
      "start": 573.737,
      "end": 578.009,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it must needs be that the power of God must be with him,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 156
    },
    {
      "start": 578.189,
      "end": 582.09,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even unto his commanding you that ye must obey.",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 157
    },
    {
      "start": 582.27,
      "end": 585.056,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, it was not he,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 158
    },
    {
      "start": 585.236,
      "end": 588.858,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but it was the Spirit of the Lord which was in him,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 159
    },
    {
      "start": 589.038,
      "end": 593.357,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which opened his mouth to utterance that he could not shut it.",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 160
    },
    {
      "start": 594.037,
      "end": 598.774,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now my son, Laman, and also Lemuel and Sam,",
      "verse": "1:28",
      "lineIndex": 162
    },
    {
      "start": 598.954,
      "end": 602.855,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also my sons who are the sons of Ishmael,",
      "verse": "1:28",
      "lineIndex": 163
    },
    {
      "start": 603.035,
      "end": 608.979,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, if ye will hearken unto the voice of Nephi ye shall not perish.",
      "verse": "1:28",
      "lineIndex": 164
    },
    {
      "start": 609.159,
      "end": 611.806,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And if ye will hearken unto him",
      "verse": "1:28",
      "lineIndex": 165
    },
    {
      "start": 611.986,
      "end": 614.029,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I leave unto you a blessing,",
      "verse": "1:28",
      "lineIndex": 166
    },
    {
      "start": 614.209,
      "end": 616.485,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even my first blessing.",
      "verse": "1:28",
      "lineIndex": 167
    },
    {
      "start": 617.165,
      "end": 619.533,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But if ye will not hearken unto him",
      "verse": "1:29",
      "lineIndex": 168
    },
    {
      "start": 619.713,
      "end": 621.803,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I take away my first blessing,",
      "verse": "1:29",
      "lineIndex": 169
    },
    {
      "start": 621.983,
      "end": 626.859,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even my blessing, and it shall rest upon him.",
      "verse": "1:29",
      "lineIndex": 170
    },
    {
      "start": 627.539,
      "end": 630.279,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, Zoram, I speak unto you:",
      "verse": "1:30",
      "lineIndex": 171
    },
    {
      "start": 630.459,
      "end": 633.617,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, thou art the servant of Laban;",
      "verse": "1:30",
      "lineIndex": 172
    },
    {
      "start": 633.797,
      "end": 638.58,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless, thou hast been brought out of the land of Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "1:30",
      "lineIndex": 173
    },
    {
      "start": 638.76,
      "end": 644.565,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I know that thou art a true friend unto my son, Nephi, forever.",
      "verse": "1:30",
      "lineIndex": 174
    },
    {
      "start": 645.245,
      "end": 648.31,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, because thou hast been faithful",
      "verse": "1:31",
      "lineIndex": 175
    },
    {
      "start": 648.49,
      "end": 651.648,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "thy seed shall be blessed with his seed,",
      "verse": "1:31",
      "lineIndex": 176
    },
    {
      "start": 651.828,
      "end": 656.611,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they dwell in prosperity long upon the face of this land;",
      "verse": "1:31",
      "lineIndex": 177
    },
    {
      "start": 656.791,
      "end": 661.11,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and nothing, save it shall be iniquity among them,",
      "verse": "1:31",
      "lineIndex": 178
    },
    {
      "start": 661.29,
      "end": 664.309,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall harm or disturb their prosperity",
      "verse": "1:31",
      "lineIndex": 179
    },
    {
      "start": 664.489,
      "end": 667.136,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "upon the face of this land forever.",
      "verse": "1:31",
      "lineIndex": 180
    },
    {
      "start": 667.816,
      "end": 671.717,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, if ye shall keep the commandments of the Lord,",
      "verse": "1:32",
      "lineIndex": 181
    },
    {
      "start": 671.897,
      "end": 676.959,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Lord hath consecrated this land for the security of thy seed",
      "verse": "1:32",
      "lineIndex": 182
    },
    {
      "start": 677.139,
      "end": 678.718,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with the seed of my son.",
      "verse": "1:32",
      "lineIndex": 183
    }
  ]
}